snippet.description:

Welcome to the Beginning. 

Letâ€™s celebrate the IMMORTAL story of Rama v/s Ravana. 

Our Truth. Our History.

Directed by Nitesh Tiwari, Produced by Namit Malhotraâ€™s Prime Focus Studios and 8-time Oscar winning VFX studio DNEG in association with Yashâ€™s Monster Mind Creations; Ramayana is being filmed for IMAX and will release worldwide: Part 1 on Diwali 2026 and Part 2 on Diwali 2027.

snippet.description:
Here's the Trailer of #HariHaraVeeraMallu Part 1: Sword vs Spirit ~ Battle for Dharma, in Theatres July 24th, 2025

Presenting you #PSPK garu in & as #HariHaraVeeraMallu! A Film by Jyothi Krisna & Produced by A Dayakar Rao under Mega Surya Production. Music is composed by Oscar-winning MM Keeravaani and presented by AM Rathnam.

I became a father and Alhamdulillah, itâ€™s a baby boy.

The moment I heard his first cry, something inside me shifted. A love I never knew existed was born. Itâ€™s hard to put into words what it feels like, but I tried capturing every moment, every emotion, and every heartbeat.

This video holds one of the most precious memories of my life. The arrival of my son. The nervousness, the joy, the tears, and the silent prayers.

Thank you for being a part of this journey. Your love and duas mean more than words can ever say.

This is the beginning of something truly beautiful. Do remember us in your prayers.âœ¨

snippet.title: Raj Thackeray Speech Funny Punch : à¤°à¤¾à¤œ à¤ à¤¾à¤•à¤°à¥‡à¤‚à¤šà¥à¤¯à¤¾ à¤ªà¤‚à¤šà¤µà¤° Supriya Sule, Rashmi Thackeray à¤–à¤³à¤–à¤³à¥‚à¤¨ à¤¹à¤¸à¤²à¥à¤¯à¤¾
snippet.description:
The Thackeray brothers' victory rally is being held today at the NSCI Dome in Worli. Preparations are in full swing for this rally. It has been reported that only the Thackeray brothers will be on the stage at the victory rally. Their victory rally is being considered important in the backdrop of the municipal elections. Adoor Bhavani (1927 â€“ 25 October 2009) was an Indian actress in Malayalam cinema, best known for her appearance in the National Award-winning film Chemmeen (1965), directed by Ramu Kariat. She had acted in about 450 films, including Mudiyanaya Puthran, Thulabharam, Kallichellamma, and Anubhavangal Paalichakal. Her last film was K. Madhu-directed Sethurama Iyer CBI. She was also a stage actress and was associated with popular theatre group KPAC.

Bhavani was born in Adoor in Travancore.Her sister, Adoor Pankajam, was also a Malayalam film actress. Adoor Bhavani died on 25 October 2009.

Adoor Bhavani (1927 â€“ 25 October 2009) was an Indian actress in Malayalam cinema, best known for her appearance in the National Award-winning film Chemmeen (1965), directed by Ramu Kariat. She had acted in about 450 films, including Mudiyanaya Puthran, Thulabharam, Kallichellamma, and Anubhavangal Paalichakal. Her last film was K. Madhu-directed Sethurama Iyer CBI. She was also a stage actress and was associated with popular theatre group KPAC.

Bhavani was born in Adoor in Travancore.Her sister, Adoor Pankajam, was also a Malayalam film actress. Adoor Bhavani died on 25 October 2009.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Vela vela vennelantha
Meedha vaali velugunantha
Moyamante nenu entha.. Arereâ€¦
Chinni gunde unnadhentha
Haayi nimpi gaalinantha
Oodhamante oopirentha.. Arereâ€¦
Kallu rendu pusthakaalu

Choopulone ardhamayye.. Anni maataluâ€¦
Mundhu leni aanavaalu
Leniponi kaaranaalu
Kotha kotha onamaalu.. Enni maayaluâ€¦
Kathalenno cheppaaru
Kavithalni raasaaru
Kaalaalu dhaataaru
Yuddhaalu chesaaru
Premalo.. Thappu ledhu premalo.. || 2 ||

Charanam 1:
Aakaasham thaakaali ani undha
Naatho raa chupisthaa aa saradhaa
Nelanthaa chuttese veelundhaa
Emundhi premisthe saripodhaa
Aha mabbulanni kommalai
Poolavaana pampithe
Aa vaana peru prema le
Dhaani ooru manamu le
Ye manasuni yemadagaku ye rujuvini.. Oh.. Anthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

Charanam 2:
Enthunte entantaa dhooraalu
Rekkallaa ayipothe paadhaalu
Unnaayaa bandhinche dhaaraalu
Oohallo untunte praanaalu
Are ningi loni chukkale
Kindhakochi cherithe
Avi neeku edhuru nilipithe
Undipova ikkade
Jaabili itu cherenu porapaatuna ani.. Oh.. Inthe.. Oh..
|| Kathalenno ||

Yuddhaalu chesaaru

snippet.title: Tag Awara Ke (Official Video) Amanraj Gill, Shivani Yadav, Shiva Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2024
snippet.description:
Tag Awara Ke (Official Video) Amanraj Gill, Shivani Yadav, Shiva Choudhary | New Haryanvi Song 2024

Nav Haryanvi Presenting "Tag Awara Ke (Official Video)" a New Haryanvi Songs Haryanavi 2024. Sung by Amanraj Gill and Shiva Choudhary. Starring with Shivani Yadav. Lyrics are Penned by Amanraj Gill. Music given by Amanraj Gill. Music Label by Nupur Audio.

Susbscribe  @NavHaryanvi  

#tagawarake #amanrajgill #shivaniyadav #shivachoudhary #navharyanvi #haryanvi #haryanvisong #haryanvisongs #haryanvisongsharyanavi #haryanvigane #newharyanvisong #latestharyanvisong #hrsong #newharyanvisongsharyanavi2024 

Lyrics : 
Oh thare laagale kyon sharey aam ye tag awara ke
Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke

Kade pahada mein kade akhada mein ravein dere yaaran ke
Thare 2 number ke kaam nire taqleefaan aale rey


Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Kyun itne masle rakhey
Aatma rakhey kashti mein
Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein


Jo khatkhyaa jaan drishti mein
Woh paaya nahi shrishti mein
Maare khoon ubaaley taate
Lade jawani aale jaatey

Tadke mare sapate
Chhorey paale chhaley rey

Gaadi ke number pe satte 
Raakhe dass dass gela patthey
Khele zindagi gele satte
Naa kaam shareefaan aale re

Gaadi mein karwa ke hooter
Rakhu gel bithake shooter
Maara raah rokan je chahiye
Jaiye sey chhati mein gaadey rey

Chaale saare ye theke aa tola banau
Kara deve hain saare callan pe kaam
Maahri nyaari hain line ji me laagde na jaam
Kyon leve bhadak le baba ka naam

Rupiya naa rakhte hum locker mein madam
Duniyaa ne mane thokkar pe madam
Hawa mein rehna toh banta hain zindagi mein
Chhattaan pe utre jinke helicopter hain madam

Positive chhora konya tootti smile
Easy schedule rave kaan pe mobile
Maare kharchein ne charche ne parche ne dekh
Khule lokkaan de munh band ho jaa se thaa hi

Tu ravey udatta note yaari mein
Tanne jodyaa ke
Kothiyan car-aan wala dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki

Kothiyan car-aan aale dharti ae
Vaas crore-aan ki
Note-aan ki bhar ri almaari
Kade pajero kade safari

Buddhi amne teri anaari
Kadi naa tenta taale rey

PARWARISH â€“ The most-watched Pakistani drama of the season, Parwarish is a gripping tale of generational conflict, where love becomes control and independence feels like rebellion. As parents hold tight to cultural traditions and children chase dreams of freedom, misunderstandings shake the very foundation of the family. Itâ€™s a powerful reflection of the emotional battles playing out in households across Pakistan today.


Samar Jafri as Wali Jahangir:
Wali, the eldest son of Jahangir, is the emotional heart of Parwarish. Handsome, intelligent, and kind-hearted, Wali was raised in the freedom of America. He dreams of becoming a musician, but his fatherâ€™s disapproval casts a long shadow. Now back in Pakistan, Wali must navigate a world where parental expectations and personal dreams collide, sparking the dramaâ€™s central conflict.

Aina Asif as Maya:
Maya, a bright and determined girl from a conservative, middle-class family, is ready to take on the world. Beautiful and self-assured, she aspires to become a doctorâ€”a path her family supports only conditionally. Caught between love, ambition, and tradition, Maya embodies the struggle of many young women in todayâ€™s society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Charity or Showbiz? | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
In this short video, we reflect on a growing concern within our churches,  are we truly giving from the heart, or are we more concerned about our name being announced in public? Too often, people give generously to the church just to gain recognition, while neglecting genuine needs like community development or council initiatives that benefit everyone.

Letâ€™s pause and ask ourselves: Is our giving rooted in love, faith, and responsibility â€” or is it driven by pride and empty tradition? True giving is quiet, sincere, and purposeful.

snippet.description:
#YeRishtaKyaKehelataHai #YRKKH #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #abhira #armaan 

*Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai* is a long-running Indian television drama that explores family relationships, love, and societal dynamics through its evolving storylines. The show, which began with Akshara and Naitik's journey, has progressed through generations, maintaining its core theme of familial bonds. In the current track, the focus has shifted to a new generation, highlighting the lives of Abhira (the union of Abhimanyu and Akshara's legacy), Armaan, and Ruhi. These characters navigate their relationships, ambitions, and the challenges of their lineage while upholding the values of the Goenka and Birla families. The blend of drama, emotions, and cultural nuances continues to resonate with viewers, ensuring its enduring popularity.

Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. Presenting you the latest updates and daily dose of entertainment in the form of star cast interviews, gossips, updates of reality shows, behind the scenes, twist in serials. Join the non stop entertainment with Saas Bahu aur Saazish for all the cool and juicy news.

snippet.description:
Sweet Corn Cutlet Recipe #corncutlet â€“ Banayein crispy aur chatpate Corn Cutlet ya Sweet Corn Kebab Tikki, jo perfect hai Evening Snacks Recipe ke liye! Is Corn Cutlet Recipe mein milega soft filling, crispy outer layer aur restaurant-style crunch. Chahe aap ise Corn Patties, Sweet Corn Vada, ya Corn Kabab Recipe ke naam se banayein â€“ taste sab mein super yummy hai! Full video mein seekhiye how to make crispy corn kebab recipe with simple steps and kitchen ingredients. 

Preparation time - 20 minutes
Serving - 8

Ingredients : 
Raw Corn - 2 pcs
Carrot - 2 small pcs
Capsicum 
Ginger-Green Chili-Garlic Paste - 1 tbsp
Chopped Coriander
Coriander Powder - 1 tbsp
Turmeric - 2 pinch
Red Chilli Powder - 1 tsp
Cumin Powder - 1/2 tsp
Garam Masala - 1/2 tsp
Amchur Powder - 1 tsp
Salt as per Taste
Black Salt - 1/2 tsp
Gram Flour - 1/2 cup
Rice Flour - 3 tbsp
